T02TD3772E:174b-1: tsa t'u r'a dza ma h'a ba lim n'a ma /
T02TD3772E:174b-3: rgyal po chen po bzhi'i gtor ma zhes bya ba /
T02TD3772E:174b-4: lha mo sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3772E:174b-5: yon tan rgyud la skye ba yi //
T02TD3772E:174b-6: bar chad sel ba'i gtor ma'i mchog / rgyal chen bzhi yi gtor ma brtsam //
T02TD3772E:174b-7: de nas sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga tshad med pa bzhin byang chub kyi sems bsgoms la /
T02TD3772E:174b-8: gtor ma khyad par du bya ba bzang du bshams pa la /
T02TD3772E:174b-9: de nas rang khyad par du bya ba yi dam gyi lhar bsgoms la /
T02TD3772E:174b-10: sku gsung thugs yi ges byin gyis brlab /
T02TD3772E:174b-11: gtor ma sva bh'a ba'i sngags kyis stong bar bsgoms la /
T02TD3772E:174b-12: stong pa'i ngang las lam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor /
T02TD3772E:175a-0: de'i steng du ram las me'i @175a * //
T02TD3772E:175a-2: aa las thod pa'i phor pa /
T02TD3772E:175a-3: de'i nang du aa zhu ba las bdud rtsi /
T02TD3772E:175a-4: de nas khru gang tsam na aa las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h'um dkar po yongs su gyur pa las rdo rjed kar po rtse lda pa khong gseng can de'i steng na /
T02TD3772E:175a-5: aa las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su t'am ljang gu las 'od zer thur la 'phros /
T02TD3772E:175a-6: bdud rtsir zhu yar 'phros sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i thugs ka nas ye shes kyi bdud rtse char rgan po tsam bab par bsams la aa k'a ro'i sngags lnga'am bdun brjod aa:h'um yang lnga'am bdun brjod /
T02TD3772E:175a-7: de ni gtor ma khyad par du bya ba'o //
T02TD3772E:175a-8: de nas mgron khyad par du bya ba ni mdun gyi nam mkha' la pam las padma'i gdan 'dab ma bzhi pa /
T02TD3772E:175a-9: lte ba la aa las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor de'i steng du t'am yig ljang gu las 'od spro bsdu byas pas autpa la t'am gyis mtshan pa /
T02TD3772E:175a-10: de las 'do 'phros tshur 'dus pas rje btsun ma sgrol ma zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3772E:175a-11: sku mdo ga ljang gu g-yas skyabs sbyin /
T02TD3772E:175a-12: g-yon pa sdong bu dang bcas pa'i autpal 'dzin pa bsam /
T02TD3772E:175a-13: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs la dza:h'um bam ho:sa bstim /
T02TD3772E:175a-14: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ges byin gyis brlab /
T02TD3772E:175a-15: de nas shar gyi padma la rgyal po yul 'khor skyong zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3772E:175a-17: lho'i padma la rgyal po 'phags skyes po sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
T02TD3772E:175a-18: nub kyi padma la rgyal po mig mi bzang sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3772E:175a-19: byang gi padma la rgyal po rnam thos sras sku mdog ser po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3772E:175a-20: de bzhi skad cig la wal gyis bskyed la /
T02TD3772E:175a-21: de nas snying gnas 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes sems dpa' dgug gzhug bya /
T02TD3772E:175a-22: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ges byin gyis brlab /
T02TD3772E:175a-23: de nas de bzhi'i ljags mi dmigs pa las yi ge h'um re yongs su gyur pa las /
T02TD3772E:175a-24: lce stod rdo rje lce smad sbu gu can gyis gtor ma la tar gyis btsugs nas gsol bar bsams la /
T02TD3772E:175a-25: ba lim ta kh'a hi zhes la na gsum bstab po//
T02TD3772E:175a-26: de nas bka' bsgo ba ni shar phyogs dri za'i gdon dang /
T02TD3772E:175a-27: lho phyogs gshen rje'i gdon dang /
T02TD3772E:175a-28: nub phyogs grul bum gyi gdon dang /
T02TD3772E:175a-29: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gyi gdon dang /
T02TD3772E:175a-30: gdon chen po bco brgyad dang /
T02TD3772E:175a-31: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu la sogs pa la bsrung du gsol zhes gsol pa gdab po //
T02TD3772E:175b-0: de nas ye shes @175b sems dpa' gshegs /
T02TD3772E:175b-1: dam tshig sems dpa' me dmigs par bsam /
T02TD3772E:175b-2: gtor ma sa gtsang sar bskyal /
T02TD3772E:175b-3: rgyal po chen po bzhi'i gtor ma rdzogs so /
T02TD3772E:175b-5: // / pandi ta d'ipam ka ra shr'i dzny'a na dang /
T02TD3772E:175b-6: lo ts'a ba dge bshes ston pas bsgyur ba'o//
